🍳 ATeam Machine Task — Frontend

LiveDemo :https://a-team-machine-task.vercel.app/

This is the frontend of the ATeam Machine Task project, developed by Muhammed Aadil NV.
It showcases a modern recipe dashboard built using React, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and Framer Motion, focusing on smooth UI animations, responsiveness, and clean architecture.

🧩 Tech Stack
Category	Technologies Used
Frontend Framework	React + TypeScript
Styling	Tailwind CSS
Animations	Framer Motion
Icons	Lucide React
State Management	React Hooks

src/
├── components/          # Reusable UI components (cards, badges, etc.)
├── pages/               # Page-level components
├── utils/               # Helper functions (e.g. getDietTypeIcon)
├── assets/              # Images and icons
├── interface/           # TypeScript interfaces
├── App.tsx              # Root app component
└── main.tsx             # App entry point


⚙️ Installation & Setup

1.Clone the repository

git clone https://github.com/aadil-nv/ATeam-Machine-Task.git


2.Navigate into the frontend directory

cd frontend


3.Install dependencies

npm install

4.Start the development server

npm run dev


🧠 Features

✅ Clean and responsive UI
✅ Interactive recipe cards with flipping animation
✅ Dynamic difficulty badges and ratings
✅ Smooth hover transitions using Framer Motion
✅ Themed components using Tailwind gradients
✅ Modular and reusable component design


